<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Aid2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Aid,</orth> vb., to assist: <cit><quote>to a. me with thy counsel,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.4.185" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. II, 4, 185</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.5.150" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 5, 150</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 5.1.20" default="NO" valid="yes">All's V, 1, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.21" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 2, 21</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.3.44" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 3, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 5.3.7" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.5.76" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 5, 76</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 2.2.63" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 II, 2, 63</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.93" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.6.66" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor I, 6, 66</bibl>.<lb />Absolutely: <cit><quote>heaven --ing,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 4.4.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Alls IV, 4, 12</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>deny her --ing hand,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.96" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 96</bibl></cit>. With an inf.: <cit><quote>--ed to expose the child,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 5.2.77" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. V, 2, 77</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>